OL,3,C'Liz was my right arm': Woman running
OL,4,CLondon Marathon for late best friend
OL,6,FA woman from is gearing up for next
OL,7,Fweekend's London Marathon in memory of
OL,8,Fher "right arm" best friend who died
OL,9,Fof cancer last year.
OL,11,FCathy Hammond is taking on the
OL,12,Fchallenge to raise money for the
OL,13,Fhospice that looked after her friend,
OL,14,FLiz Finch, in her final days.
OL,16,FLiz spent the final six weeks of her
OL,17,Flife at Sue Ryder Leckhampton Court
OL,18,FHospice before losing her battle with
OL,19,Fsuspected bile duct cancer aged 46, in
OL,20,FJune 2023.
