OL,3,C'Liz was my right arm': Woman running
OL,4,CLondon Marathon for late best friend
OL,6,FCathy remembers her friend, who was a
OL,7,Fkeen runner, as "funny, strong and an
OL,8,Famazing mother.
OL,10,F"Liz was my right arm, our left arm -
OL,11,Fshe was just part of our friendship
OL,12,Fgroup that you could just tell
OL,13,Feverything and anything to and it was
OL,14,Fa safe space. There's a big gap left
OL,15,Fsince her passing," she told ITV News.
OL,17,FThey had been friends for over 20
OL,18,Fyears and Liz would refer to Cathy and
OL,19,Fsome of her other friends as the
OL,20,F"adventure buddies" - but their time
OL,21,Ftogether was sadly cut short.
