OL,3,C'Liz was my right arm': Woman running
OL,4,CLondon Marathon for late best friend
OL,6,F- All for the hospice that made Liz's
OL,7,Ffinal days so special.
OL,9,F"The care that she received from
OL,10,Feverybody from the volunteers, to the
OL,11,Factual nurses - the whole team for Liz
OL,12,Fand her family - was amazing," Cathy
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,15,F"Small things like having a foot
OL,16,Fmassage, her nails painted, just
OL,17,Fhelped lift her on some really dark
OL,18,Fdays."
OL,20,FWith under a week to go Cathy says Liz
OL,21,Fis at the forefront of her mind.
