OL,3,C'Liz was my right arm': Woman running
OL,4,CLondon Marathon for late best friend
OL,6,FShe added: "Liz would say it's just me
OL,7,Fall over, biting off a little bit more
OL,8,Fthan I can chew but definitely
OL,9,Fsticking with it."
OL,11,FEllie Bailey, Clinical Team Leader at
OL,12,FLeckhampton Court Hospice says
OL,13,Ffundraising plays a vital role in
OL,14,Fhelping people make the best they
OL,15,Fpossibly can of their last days.
OL,17,FShe said: "We provide palliative care
OL,18,Ffor people who are at the start of
OL,19,Ftheir journeys or the end.
